  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess in France the impact of Prevenar on the possible evolution
      of the pneumococcal serotypes distribution and antibiotic resistance in NP samples of
      children with AOM.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
